{"tid":790790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[串鳩香港IT Plan]美國巨企招聘不再重視「大學學位」","createTime":"2018-08-23T09:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T12:13:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"18c879bf5181c8a92020611b472051a40c78dbad","tid":790790,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，根據近期美國知名求職資訊網站Glassdoor數據顯示，排名首15家企業僱主已不再要求應徵者擁有「大學學士學位」，包括港人熟悉的Google、蘋果公司(Apple Inc,)、國際商業機器(IBM)、安永(EY)等。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，IBM副主席Joanna Daley在2017年接受媒體訪問時已表示，IBM差不多有15%員工沒有大學文憑，目前該公司更專注找到有「實際經驗」的人才。<br />\n<br />\n以下是招聘時不注意大學學位的企業：<br />\n<br />\n1、【科技】Google<br />\n2、【會計】安永(Ernst and Young)<br />\n3、【出版商】企鵝蘭登書屋(Penguin Random House)<br />\n4、【零售批發】好市多(Costco Wholesale)<br />\n5、【超市】全食超市(Whole Foods)<br />\n6、【酒店】希爾頓(Hilton)<br />\n7、【超市】大眾超級市場(Publix) <br />\n8、【科技】蘋果公司(Apple)<br />\n9、【咖啡店】星巴克(Starbucks)<br />\n10、【百貨】諾德斯特龍(Nordstrom) <br />\n11、【家品】家得寶(Home Depot)<br />\n12、【科技】國際商業機器(IBM)<br />\n13、【金融】美國銀行(Bank of America)<br />\n14、【快餐】Chipotle<br />\n15、【零售】勞氏(Lowe's)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180823/bkn-20180823164336306-0823_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180823%2Fbkn-20180823164336306-0823_00842_001.html&d=t1PXMhj4yW7L02zRJ6hr9i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f69f86a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180823/bkn-20180823164336306-0823_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"39b869a0acb37ff1bc25c6b51fb721a6771e0003","tid":790790,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299a5910fe23f069805f89bddc28b2171d9aae74","tid":790790,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyT